00:01:16.740 --> 00:01:21.070
The Kingda Ka in Jackson New Jersey holds
the record for tallest roller coaster with

00:01:21.070 --> 00:01:25.810
the main top hat tower reaching 456 feet.

00:01:25.810 --> 00:01:31.850
After a 90 degree roll to the right it reaches
the peak and then drops 418 feet down through

00:01:31.850 --> 00:01:35.120
