year 2000, which was "The Year of the Dragon".

00:02:02.810 --> 00:02:09.649
It holds the record for the longest track
length at 8,133 feet and 2 inches.

00:02:09.649 --> 00:02:14.170
Because the construction required so much
steel for earthquake protection it cost over

00:02:14.170 --> 00:02:17.390
50 million dollars to build.

